title: [Vornavian Coast, Beached Hulk]
description: The port side rail has been broken through completely while the rail to starboard is still intact, and overlooks a view of the beach and coastal cliffs.  The mizzenmast reaches high above the deck, which continues northeast to the bow and southwest to stern.

The port side rail has been broken through completely while the rail to starboard is still intact, and overlooks a view of the beach and coastal cliffs.  The mizzenmast reaches high above the deck, which continues northeast to the bow and southwest to stern.  A pattern of blackened scars spirals up the mizzenmast.
